OL,3,CMan who found migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cshocked to be hit with Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FA Gloucestershire lorry driver, who
OL,8,Falerted the authorities to stowaways
OL,9,Fwhen he was coming back from France,
OL,10,Fis battling to get them to drop a
OL,11,F#12,000 fine.
OL,13,FMichael Fletcher, 63, from the Forest
OL,14,Fof Dean, says he is facing debt
OL,15,Fcollectors and is being penalised by
OL,16,Fthe Border Force "for doing the right
OL,17,Fthing".
