OL,3,CMan who found migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cshocked to be hit with Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FMr Fletcher says he was advised by
OL,8,Fofficers that he had done all the
OL,9,Fnecessary checks. But was shocked to
OL,10,Freceive a letter from the Border Force
OL,11,Fin February demanding payment of
OL,12,F#12,000.
OL,14,FThey claimed in the letter that Mr
OL,15,FFletcher was unable to produce a
OL,16,Fchecklist at the time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/20
