OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1728320733
OL,3,CMan who found migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cshocked to be hit with Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FBut after disputing this, and
OL,8,Fproviding a photograph which shows his
OL,9,Fchecklist, Border Force are now
OL,10,Fseeking a payment for a reduced fine
OL,11,Fof #3,000.
OL,13,FBut Mr Fletcher says he is wrongly
OL,14,Fbeing targeted for doing the right
OL,15,Fthing and does not see why he should
OL,16,Fpay for not doing anything wrong.
OL,18,FHe believes he has been sent the fine
OL,19,Fbecause border guards did not do their
OL,20,Fwork correctly.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/20
