OL,3,CMan who found migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cshocked to be hit with Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FHe is stressed by the situation and
OL,8,Fhas had to change his job in the
OL,9,Fmeantime and only works in
OL,10,Ftransportation within the UK.
OL,12,F"I refuse to pay for a fine when I've
OL,13,Fdone nothing wrong," he said.
OL,15,FMr Fletcher said he had passed the
OL,16,Fsecurity checks at the UK Immigration
OL,17,FControl Zone in Calais and was about
OL,18,Fto board the ferry when he felt a
OL,19,Fsuspicious movement in the back of his
OL,20,Florry.
