OL,7,FHe said: "The two vehicles in front of
OL,8,Fme started their engines and I then
OL,9,Ffelt my lorry move which was strange
OL,10,Fas it was a sunny day and there was no
OL,11,Fwind.
OL,13,F"I did all the checks. I walked around
OL,14,Fto the front and I thought the only
OL,15,Fplace now is up on the roof, and
OL,16,Fthat's four metres high.
OL,26,@oD@JOUuD@AOU
