OL,3,CMan who found migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cshocked to be hit with Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,F"So I climbed up between the lorry cab
OL,8,Fand I managed to get my hands on top
OL,9,Fand pull myself up, and I looked over
OL,10,Fand I could see tape where they cut
OL,11,Fthe roof and somebody had sealed it
OL,12,Fback with tape.
OL,14,F"So I got down and I shouted to the
OL,15,FFrench border guards and they came
OL,16,Fback with the dog. I told them I
OL,17,Fthought I had somebody on board. Then
OL,18,Fabout 30 minutes later the English
OL,19,FBorder Force came.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
