OL,3,CMan who found migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cshocked to be hit with Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,F"They had the paperwork off the French
OL,8,Fand the English officer started to
OL,9,Ftake notes and he took photos of my
OL,10,Fchecklist.
OL,12,F"I had a book and I took that photo
OL,13,Fbecause I thought he was going to take
OL,14,Fthe book off me.
OL,16,F"He held on to the book after taking
OL,17,Fphotos. He looked at my insurance and
OL,18,Fall my other documents, my licences
OL,19,Fand all that.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
