OL,3,CMan who found migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cshocked to be hit with Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,F"That was all in order and then they
OL,8,Fopened up and they had two people on
OL,9,Fboard.
OL,11,F"The English officer was looking at my
OL,12,Fpaperwork checking my insurance, all
OL,13,Fthat. And then he said it's nearly
OL,14,Ftime for me to finish.
OL,16,F"I've got some officers coming down
OL,17,Fand I will hand it all over to them.
OL,18,FSo they came down.
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@AOU
