OL,3,CMan who found migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cshocked to be hit with Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,F"He ended the paperwork. But he didn't
OL,8,Fhand the camera over with the photos
OL,9,Fon.
OL,11,F"So that is where the photos must have
OL,12,Fbeen mislaid because he finished his
OL,13,Fshift and we had to wait another hour
OL,14,Fand a half for the Calais police to
OL,15,Fcome in to have those immigrants taken
OL,16,Fout and let go again before they'd
OL,17,Frelease me.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
