OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,F"The police came, they took the
OL,8,Fimmigrants. The UK Border Force said,
OL,9,F'Oh, here you are. Here's your
OL,10,Fpaperwork. You can go now.'"
OL,12,FMr Fletcher said he was asked by the
OL,13,Fofficers where he had parked the night
OL,14,Fbefore.
OL,16,FHe explained that it was in the Calais
OL,17,Fregistered truck stop that the
OL,18,Fgovernment recommends drivers should
OL,19,Fpark at.
