OL,7,FHe says the officer told him they had
OL,8,Fhad found several stowaways in
OL,9,Fvehicles that had come from that site
OL,10,Frecently.
OL,12,FMr Fletcher was returning to the UK
OL,13,Fvia France with a delivery from a
OL,14,Ffactory in Germany.
OL,16,FHe says he doesn't understand how the
OL,17,Fsecurity did not detect the stowaways.
