OL,3,CMan who found migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cshocked to be hit with Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FMr Fletcher raised this issue with his
OL,8,FCounty Councillor Philip Robinson
OL,9,F(Con, Mitcheldean) earlier this year
OL,10,Fwho suggested he speak with his then
OL,11,FMP Mark Harper.
OL,13,FMr Harper had raised the issue with
OL,14,Fthen Home Secretary James Cleverly who
OL,15,Fwas in the process of looking into the
OL,16,Fissue.
OL,18,FThis stalled after Parliament was
OL,19,Fdissolved and his MP lost his seat and
OL,20,Fis no longer dealing with his case.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/20
