OL,3,CMan who found migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cshocked to be hit with Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FHe has since been unable to get the
OL,8,Fnew Forest of Dean MP Matt Bishop to
OL,9,Flook into his case.
OL,11,FHe said: "I just want my issue
OL,12,Fresolved. I'm now waiting for bailiffs
OL,13,Fto come take the value of the fine.
OL,15,F"I don't understand how they can fine
OL,16,Fme when they haven't taken me to court.
OL,18,F"The first letter they sent to me was
OL,19,Fhow to pay the fine and nobody wants
OL,20,Fto talk to me because I'm not that
OL,21,Fimportant."
OL,26,@sD@JOUwD@AOUzD@AOU}D@KO]
