OL,3,CMan who found migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cshocked to be hit with Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FCllr Robinson said he had every
OL,8,Fconfidence that it was going to be
OL,9,Fdealt with.
OL,11,FHe said: "There's no way Mark would
OL,12,Fnot have got a result in that, as far
OL,13,Fas I'm concerned, I know it was a slam
OL,14,Fdunk.
OL,16,F"I've been only too pleased to play my
OL,17,Fpart in helping Fletch but where we
OL,18,Fare now is extremely frustrating due
OL,19,Fto the complete absence of help from
OL,20,Fthe new MP for the Forest of Dean,
OL,21,FMatt Bishop.
OL,26,@sD@JOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/20
