OL,3,CMan who found migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cshocked to be hit with Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,F"Had Mark been re-elected in July, all
OL,8,Fwould have been well and Fletch would
OL,9,Fhave been freed of his stressful and
OL,10,Funnecessary burden."
OL,12,FMr Bishop's office confirmed they had
OL,13,Fbeen contacted by Mr Fletcher.
OL,15,FHowever, they say they cannot deal
OL,16,Fwith casework from constituents
OL,17,Fwithout their postal address.
OL,19,FThey also said they have not received
OL,20,Fany information from Mr Harper or Cllr
OL,21,FRobinson.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@TO]
