OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,F"I would be very happy to have a
OL,8,Fmeeting with the constituent and Cllr
OL,9,FRobinson to look into this case and
OL,10,Fencourage them both to contact my team
OL,11,Fso that this can be set up," Mr Bishop
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FThe law changed in 2023 during the
OL,15,Fprevious Conservative Government and
OL,16,Fincreased fines, new maximum penalty
OL,17,Flevels and a new penalty for failing
OL,18,Fto adequately secure a goods vehicle
OL,19,Fcame into force to prevent dangerous
OL,20,Fand illegal journeys to the UK.
